reviewText: The wrong one was sent. I wanted season 2, not the one that was sent.
My son loves all of thaws series, good price point

I watched Casper as a child myself (60 yrs ago) and it was one of my favorite cartoons then.  I was so thrilled to find it again so I bought it for my 7 year old grandson.  He has watched this a million times and brings it with him when he comes to stay with Nana!
